---------
Two-electron parts of Vee(A,A) were calculated using the TWOe program:
The TWOe program was used for comparison purposes:
     a) Pavel M. Polestshuk, J. Comp. Chem., 34, 206 (2013)
     b) Pavel M. Polestshuk, J. Chem. Phys., 139, 054108 (2013)

